      "rationale": "Validation activities use production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs under ASTM F1717 loading — identical to the COU. Testing conducted at two independent laboratories confirms inter-laboratory reproducibility. The validation scenario is a direct analog to the regulatory submission context. Gradation 3 achieved."
